%F A398028 G.f.: x^2*(24*x^10 - 198*x^9 + 867*x^8 - 2476*x^7 + 4072*x^6 - 3896*x^5 + 2251*x^4 - 798*x^3 + 170*x^2 - 20*x + 1) / ((1-2*x) * (1-4*x)^2 * (2*x^2 - 4*x + 1) * (2*x^4 - 16*x^3 + 20*x^2 - 8*x + 1)) - x^4*(7*x^3 - 14*x^2 + 7*x - 1)^2 / ((1-4*x)^(3/2) * (1-2*x) * (2*x^2 - 4*x + 1) * (2*x^4 - 16*x^3 + 20*x^2 - 8*x + 1)) [Conway and Guttmann, 2026].
